eu_initiatives: All related to forestry and bioenergy, vocational training, competition, public procurement, social dialogue, forest certification, sustainability and biodiversity
organisation_name: European Network of Forest Entrepreneurs e.V. (ENFE)
section: II - In-house lobbyists and trade/business/professional associations
goals__remit:
ENFE is the European representation of forest entrepreneurs which are service providers for forest operations and forest management. Ordinary members are the respective national association of forest entrepreneurs. 
 
In the beginning of 2015 Enfe merged its lobbying activities with Ceettar organisation.
